1.Write a program to take a number from an input box and check whether the number is even or odd. Display the result on the webpage without using alert().

2.Write a program to take a number from the user and display its square and cube when a button is clicked.

3.Write a program to count how many times a button is clicked and display the count dynamically on the webpage.

4.Write a program to change the background color of the page randomly every time a button is clicked.

5.Write a program to display the current date, time, and day (Monday, Tuesday, etc.) on button click.

6.Write a program to take marks of three subjects from input boxes and display the total marks, average, and result (Pass/Fail).

7.Write a program to show or hide a paragraph when a button is clicked (toggle functionality).

8.Write a program to validate a text box input and display a warning message if the input field is left empty.

9.Write a program to display the largest number among three numbers entered by the user.
